{"tid":2265341,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【本地遊記】著超人拖鞋，挑戰大圓左澗小丑坑","createTime":"2020-10-31T10:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T06:29:30.000Z","uid":121784,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"663176f1522c018e2ce72a3324c556f3abaa76b5","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"買左對防滑拖鞋，20零蚊對，於是著上佢，試下行澗有幾掂，對比5 6百蚊一對既澗王之王five ten如何。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n背景資料<br />\n<br />\n「大圓左澗」370米分出的右源，因直至「相思樹徑」聞名的「小丑石」，故名「小丑坑」是澗初段為小澗風貌，但臨近「相思樹徑」，瀑流一個緊接一個，行來使人暢快。<br />\n<br />\nGPS track<br />\n&nbsp;<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ABvdHfW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FABvdHfW.jpg&h=825402b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7d0xdnD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7d0xdnD.jpg&h=e45d5dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA 龍門郊遊徑一號橋，大圓左澗入澗位<br />\nB 三叉分源位<br />\nC 小丑坑主瀑<br />\nD 相思林徑離澗位<br />\nE 相思林徑上下路交界<br />\nF 大圓左澗與相思林徑上路交界"},{"pid":"e1f754caaf51b04fb34f874e2f0716fa780ee4d4","tid":2265341,"uid":201604,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"咪能水鳩人啦 一陣班連登柒頭有樣學樣 最後又要call消防救"},{"pid":"f64bdae1cfc6a2e0d2c630528a80619c0fe27fd3","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:49:08.000Z","msg":"超人拖既樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83P2AEh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83P2AEh.png&h=a0115eac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"959daa3c5d5fe675bfa43505bedb71d14cc636f7","tid":2265341,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"巴打咩app<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894fec4a9c4784213226d9623af817553db96026","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e1f754caaf51b04fb34f874e2f0716fa780ee4d4","tid":2265341,"uid":201604,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"咪能水鳩人啦 一陣班連登柒頭有樣學樣 最後又要call消防救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"戴返個頭盔先<br />\n<br />\n小丑坑 難度3.5星 路程有不少攀爬位 不適合溯澗新手<br />\n<br />\n初玩石澗, 宜先往新手區熟習累積經驗, 如北角小馬坑、大城石澗、猴塘溪等等一兩星之石澗"},{"pid":"d70a40db3fbf2930e3087bba642da7f1d8b3f214","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"959daa3c5d5fe675bfa43505bedb71d14cc636f7","tid":2265341,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"巴打咩app<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:53:50.000Z","msg":"Viewranger"},{"pid":"8ad0b17835301746d8ff26181917a39ad4965461","tid":2265341,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d70a40db3fbf2930e3087bba642da7f1d8b3f214","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"959daa3c5d5fe675bfa43505bedb71d14cc636f7","tid":2265341,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"巴打咩app<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:53:50.000Z","msg":"Viewranger"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"Thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4382b2f6bb396e82106abf5cbabbec9e92f4174e","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:01:16.000Z","msg":"川龍起步, 呢間茶樓藍到黑, 唔係無哂HP既緊急情況, 都唔會幫襯佢.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WDJfbeO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWDJfbeO.jpg&h=3b22edb5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n川龍重狗, 估唔到第一關就係度卡住左, 對峙左成五分鐘, 最後有架的士狗, 趕走左隻黑狗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wUpBE8K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwUpBE8K.jpg&h=fd5a7870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉入龍門郊遊徑, 行多段路, 就到一號橋, 係度轉左入溯大圓左澗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D57oj82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD57oj82.jpg&h=20a48d08&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相比起大圓主澗, 大圓左澗既滕蔓多十倍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aw7SXV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faw7SXV6.jpg&h=ea2f604f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13eb4339309ddf9a3820ae17396d4fffecaba3c0","tid":2265341,"uid":343807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"想請教下巴打 係無裝嘅環境下 遇到山狗 / 養狗 <br />\n但又要局住一定向前行 應該點樣處理"},{"pid":"053ed447c9bbca761cb6be8917d79846d592bf39","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"370米高既分源位, 小丑坑請往右走. 行多幾步會再有分源位, 小丑坑靠右.<br />\n其實小丑坑, 就係大圓左澗右源<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aiCGRg8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaiCGRg8.jpg&h=a64f918d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上到流瀑頂, D石頭好大舊, 爬死人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwRcXXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwRcXXQ.jpg&h=4aadd356&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住呢條瀑好易過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RVFdHpL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRVFdHpL.jpg&h=061bf7cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後, 澗途被封死!<br />\n好彩大石左邊有位可攀上, 不過有D險, 腳位外斜, 如果對鞋跣既話就gg... 所以行澗, 千其千其千其, 要著防滑鞋!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CmiOwic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmiOwic.jpg&h=6bc36924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n通關後, 回望封澗位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxCPfKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxCPfKT.jpg&h=e68065ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6485b0a379325f320380e336d7525356d6614ece","tid":2265341,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13eb4339309ddf9a3820ae17396d4fffecaba3c0","tid