d":"13eb4339309ddf9a3820ae17396d4fffecaba3c0","tid":2265341,"uid":343807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"想請教下巴打 係無裝嘅環境下 遇到山狗 / 養狗 <br />\n但又要局住一定向前行 應該點樣處理"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:08:22.000Z","msg":"山狗唔咬人 村狗會咬人 主人唔拉走你都過唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"有時有啲村 啲人係放養啲狗 由得啲狗出黎 <br />\n個主人跟本又唔係佢身邊 我又要向前行喎 佢又企係路中心 吠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"你博佢唔咬你 聽前人講 要過就拎定棍 佢黎就打落佢個鼻/頭度 <br />\n有人試過照過俾狗咬要中途走去打破傷風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48f308bd0555fe5d6c4a0ece33e17ff36b3865a","tid":2265341,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"349af113a0f6c5d90635ac6e7daa8b4ed91bac3f","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6485b0a379325f320380e336d7525356d6614ece","tid":2265341,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13eb4339309ddf9a3820ae17396d4fffecaba3c0","tid":2265341,"uid":343807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"想請教下巴打 係無裝嘅環境下 遇到山狗 / 養狗 <br />\n但又要局住一定向前行 應該點樣處理"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:08:22.000Z","msg":"山狗唔咬人 村狗會咬人 主人唔拉走你都過唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:12:59.000Z","msg":"我怕狗, 所以會避開先, 好多時D狗都唔一定猴住你, 一陣就會走開<br />\n如果係陀地村狗就慘D..... 通常都會由唔怕狗既朋友開路, 用氣勢迫返D狗離開村徑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:16:55.000Z","msg":"梅子林之前有人養左幾隻狗又唔綁 條路正正就係要過佢新起果幾間屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd700b78897d2e1bdb874ed61637cde212ecfda","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:19:49.000Z","msg":"好快又到另一條長瀑, 右邊可小心攀上, 手腳位算OK<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLEh87t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLEh87t.jpg&h=0e3b1035&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小流瀑, 左邊可通過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5y490ep.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5y490ep.jpg&h=d1f547cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到左470米海拔左右, 就係主瀑, 好高呀!<br />\n主瀑分兩層, 第一層可以跟絲帶, 係左邊山路攀上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5tbt7T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5tbt7T.jpg&h=8b2013d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後橫移瀑右, 再攀上第二層<br />\n第二層雖然高, 但險而不危, 只要認清內斜既手腳位, 避開外斜既位, 就可以輕易攀上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2Y62tM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2Y62tM.jpg&h=d38426c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後仲有個瀑, 安全可以右邊攀上, 貪玩既可以瀑中正攀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9yyHtV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9yyHtV.jpg&h=51b4dc28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無耐流水漸收, 變成乾坑, 爬多陣會見到絲帶, 到達相思林徑, 安全達陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixjBFf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FixjBFf1.jpg&h=2e399335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回望小丑坑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bn3rh2H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbn3rh2H.jpg&h=316e53fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dc2914bf0f497236173444faaceeaf6f2ceeab3","tid":2265341,"uid":41796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"成日俾d石磨甩皮，又磨爛左幾條褲，從此以後唔行澗"},{"pid":"532e3b151f9616f068c4f8544861e34222260866","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:23:48.000Z","msg":"唔知邊個放個路牌係度, 原來相思林徑係度分開上下兩條路, 地圖記載既係上路, 下路應該係新開既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yubknuM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyubknuM.jpg&h=c642b1c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行左下路, 竟然來到大圓左澗左源既上面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTo62vn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTo62vn.jpg&h=4706a716&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好貪玩, 一於爬下左源一小段, 去返相思林徑上路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dpsokhg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdpsokhg.jpg&h=fe518c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就沿路落山, 返荃灣市中心, 搵間黃店食下午茶"},{"pid":"ed55072ad8903b524c5d1eca3d276dca50429969","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"著住呢對超人拖, 行山路落山簡直係惡夢, 結果步速好慢, 要就住就住<br />\n<br />\n總結, 呢對超人拖表現:<br />\n石澗環境/濕滑石面攀爬: 8/10, 如果唔係有機會甩拖, 差唔多比得上專業澗鞋<br />\n輕便: 8/10, 真係幾輕<br />\n車路: 5/10, 表現一般, 平時踢拖落街既feel<br />\n山路: 1/10, 鞋底薄, 零避震, 好惡頂, 落山更加係惡夢<br />\n速度Buff: -5/10, 唔駛旨意跑得快<br />\n<br />\n20零蚊一對, 算係咁啦~<br />\n不過入澗前, 離澗後, 要換返對正常波鞋或行山鞋先得"},{"pid":"218ada3f793323feb3420598458686c8846eeb1d","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7dc2914bf0f497236173444faaceeaf6f2ceeab3","tid":2265341,"uid":41796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"成日俾d石磨甩皮，又磨爛左幾條褲，從此以後唔行澗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"咁嚴重@@<br />\n如果驚磨擦甩皮, 可以戴手套<br />\nbtw我自己無用手套"},{"pid":"dc80614ca95ee9d4080b40d6fcfdb739d6a64a7a","tid":2265341,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed55072ad8903b524c5d1eca3d276dca50429969","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"著住呢對超人拖, 行山路落山簡直係惡夢, 結果步速好慢, 要就住就住<br />\n<br />\n總結, 呢對超人拖表現:<br />\n石澗環境/濕滑石面攀爬: 8/10, 如果唔係有機會甩拖, 差唔多比得上專業澗鞋<br />\n輕便: 8/10, 真係幾輕<br />\n車路: 5/10, 表現一般, 平時踢拖落街既feel<br />\n山路: 1/10, 鞋底薄, 零避震, 好惡頂, 落山更加係惡夢<br />\n速度Buff: -5/10, 唔駛旨意跑得快<br />\n<br />\n20零蚊一對, 算係咁啦~<br />\n不過入澗前, 離澗後, 要換返對正常波鞋或行山鞋先得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T15:58:14.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"146ec2d5a9d0c588f1eae8e4a976a3f1079a5f45","tid":2265341,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"超人拖實測片段：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4RgeVERDKZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4RgeVERDKZ4&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=3f67fbfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4RgeVERDKZ4</a>"}]}